string-array.name: auto_backup_information_which_contents
string-array.item: Ekwentị: oku na agụgụala ozi
Ozi: ozi emelitere, ozi mgbasa ozi na ozi ederede
Ndịnzìrịtaozī: Ndịnzìrịtaozī, adreesị ozi-e na kaadị azụmahịa echekwara na njiarụ gị
Ngụafọ: mmemme na ọrụ echekwara na njiarụ gị
Elekere: Mkpu, elekere ụwa, na ngụ oge

Mwube: nnwetaoghere mwube, ụda nkụ ekwentị̀, nhọrọ Ahụigodo Samsung, mwube Wi-Fi, Bluetooth njiarụ ndị ejikọtara, mwube njirimara ihu, mwube akara mkpịsị aka, na mwube Always On Display (a gaghị eme ụda nkụ ekwentị̀ ndabara gị nke abụọ)
Ihuenyo bé: okirikiri nhọrọ ukwuu, akwụkwọ ahụaja, na mwube Samsung DeX
Ngwa: faịlụ nnwụnye na ntọala ngwa
Ihe ndekọ olu: ndekọ
